    "en": {
      "title": "Protesters meet with party leaders",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A meeting will be held today between the parties involved in the vacating protest and the party leaders.",
        "25 people will participate in this discussion, representing the parties involved in the protest in Galle.",
        "During this meeting, which will be held in the Parliament building, views and ideas regarding future political action will be presented. (a)"
      ],
